  "title": "admin asssitant",
  "description": "<p><strong>Part-Time Admin Assistant – Yoga Studio (Hybrid)</strong></p><p><strong>Location:</strong> City Hall, Singapore (Hybrid: Work from home + occasional studio presence)<br /><strong>Working Hours:</strong> Flexible, some mornings at the studio (9 AM – 12 PM, weekdays, friday full day, rest of the day work remote )<br /><strong>Salary:</strong> $1,600 + CPF</p><p><strong>About Us:</strong><br />We are a thriving yoga studio dedicated to wellness, community, and personal growth. Our ideal admin assistant loves yoga/fitness, is passionate about supporting a smooth-running studio, and enjoys contributing to a harmonious environment.</p><p><strong>Role Overview:</strong><br />We are looking for a smart, experienced <strong>Admin Assistant</strong> to support our daily operations. This is a hybrid part-time role for someone who works for love and hobby, yet brings professionalism, organization, and years of experience.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Manage weekly class and workshop schedules, courses </p></li><li><p>Handle course and workshop registrations</p></li><li><p>Collect and organize customer feedback</p></li><li><p>Respond to inquiries and assist with marketing communications</p></li><li><p>Assist in daily admin tasks to support smooth company operations</p></li><li><p>Perform any additional tasks to support the team</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Previous admin experience  or managing such experience </p></li><li><p>Highly organized, detail-oriented, and self-motivated</p></li><li><p>Strong communication skills, able to handle customer interactions professionally</p></li><li><p>Tech-savvy and comfortable with remote work</p></li><li><p>Passion for yoga /fitss and wellness is a plus</p></li></ul><p><strong>Why Join Us:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Flexible hybrid work arrangement</p></li><li><p>Work in a positive, supportive environment</p></li><li><p>Contribute to a yoga community you love</p></li></ul>",
